%p
  Dear #{full_name(@reviewer)},

%p
  This is a friendly reminder that you've been asked to review the following #{'submission'.pluralize(@incomplete_reviews.count)} to #{link_to @grant.name, grant_url(@grant)}:
  %ul
    - @incomplete_reviews.each do |incomplete_review|
      %li
        = link_to(incomplete_review.submission.title, grant_submission_url(@grant, incomplete_review.submission))

%p
  Please complete by #{@grant.review_close_date.strftime("%B %e, %Y")}.

%p
  You may also visit the following link to view #{link_to "all your reviews for #{@grant.name}", profile_reviews_url(params: { q: { grant_name_cont: @grant.name, s: 'overall_impact_score+desc' } })} on one page.
%p
  Thank you
